data.description: Seller is offer 5k towards closing cost with full price offer. Situated in the heart of Rincon, this all brick one story home may be the perfect home.  Conveniently location to local amenities and attractions. The property offers an oversized lot, NO HOA and wood burning fireplace.Step inside to discover a mix of contemporary with warm and comfort. The charm extends outdoors, providing a delightful space for relaxation or entertainment by enjoyed the screened patio or the backyard. The 1300 square foot detached garage offers ample space for various purposes and includes power and water. All appliances are less than one year old and will remain with the property.  The washer and dryer front loaders are included with purchase.
